OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy and
OL,6,Fblustery showers continuing at first
OL,7,Fthis evening, but these gradually
OL,8,Feasing for many in the early hours.
OL,9,FStaying largely cloudy and breezy
OL,10,Fovernight, with temperatures on the
OL,11,Fmilder side.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FLargely cloudy at first on
OL,14,FWednesday, but some brighter spells
OL,15,Fdeveloping at times into the
OL,16,Fafternoon. A few spots of rain
OL,17,Fpossible where the cloud thickens,
OL,18,Fmainly over western hills.
